# Copy this file to `keys.env` and fill in values. `keys.env` is gitignored.
#
# Cineforge runs FULLY OFFLINE at render time. The only reason a token is
# needed is to DOWNLOAD gated model weights during install:
#   - black-forest-labs/FLUX.2-*        (gated, opt-in image backend)
#   - google/gemma-3-12b-it             (LTX-2.3 text encoder, opt-in video backend)
#   - some Wan / Qwen repositories       (occasionally gated)
#
# Get a token at https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens (read scope is enough).
# Leave blank if you only use the Apache/MIT default backends (Wan 2.2, Z-Image,
# Chatterbox, ACE-Step, EchoMimicV3, SeedVR2) — none of those are gated.

HF_TOKEN=
